title: Hour 3 - Overcovered and Overrated
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Overcovered and Overrated
description:
Dan Patrick discusses overcovered and overrated athletes. LA Times NBA Writer Dan Woike joins the show to break down why the Lakers traded for Patrick Beverly. Plus, what will happen next for Russell Westbrook?
